name: Marvin The Robot
description: Memecoin based on a robot character named Marvin. He is depressed, grumpy, and has some attitude. Deep down he has a good mechanical heart though, and is just looking to find some purpose and meaning in this thing we call life. What started off as just a simple memecoin idea has now evolved into a real presence as a bot in Telegram. With over 120 channels using Marvin the bot for engagement and special features.
